data.description: Welcome to this magnificent single family home in a prestigious gated community. Boasting high ceilings and hardwood floors, this property offers an elegant and spacious living environment. With 4 bd and 2.5 bth, including a screened in porch and deck perfect for enjoying the tranquil surroundings, this home provides ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The jetted tub in the master bathroom adds a luxurious touch, allowing you to unwind after a long day. Situated in a golf course community, residents can enjoy the scenic views and recreational opportunities right at their doorstep.
